ql.set_option('output_dir', output_dir)
ql.set_option('optimize', 'no')
ql.set_option('scheduler', 'ALAP')
ql.set_option('scheduler_uniform', 'yes')
ql.set_option('log_level', 'LOG_WARNING')
platform = ql.Platform(platform_name, config_fn)
p = ql.Program('test_qec', platform, num_qubits, num_cregs)
k = ql.Kernel('kernel_0', platform, num_qubits, num_cregs)
x = 7
xN = x - 5
xE = x + 1
xS = x + 5
xW = x - 1
z = 11
zN = z - 5
zE = z + 1
zS = z + 5
zW = z - 1
rdX = ql.CReg()
rdZ = ql.CReg()
k.gate('rym90', [x])
k.gate('rym90', [xN])
k.gate('rym90', [xE])
k.gate('rym90', [xW])
k.gate('rym90', [xS])
k.wait(all_qubits, 0)
k.gate('cz', [x, xE])
k.gate('cz', [x, xN])
k.gate('cz', [x, xS])
k.gate('cz', [x, xW])
k.wait(all_qubits, 0)
k.gate('ry90', [x])
k.gate('ry90', [xN])
k.gate('ry90', [xE])
k.gate('ry90', [xW])
k.gate('ry90', [xS])
k.wait(all_qubits, 0)
k.gate('measure', [x], rdX)
k.wait([x], 0)
k.gate('rym90', [z])
k.gate('cz', [z, zE])
k.gate('cz', [z, zS])
k.gate('cz', [z, zN])
k.gate('cz', [z, zW])
k.gate('ry90', [z])
k.gate('measure', [z], rdZ)
p.add_kernel(k)
p.compile()
unittest.skip
